          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又只见刘能到跟前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘能",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报，报，报，报与姑娘你知道。山下来了一员将，威风凛凛甚年少。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘能",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "白盔白甲白旗号，凶猛非常赛虎豹。跨下一骑白鬃马，手提银枪光耀耀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘能",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他说他姓高，他要想把山寨洗平了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一同追上前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四下手、四女兵、刘能、刘金定同转场。四龙套、四上手引高俊保同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喽兵一齐往前进，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要与来将动刀兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘金定、高俊保同打过合，比式子。四龙套、四下手、四女兵、四龙套、四上手同哦那个钻烟筒下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "问声小将通名姓，"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "高俊保就是你少爷的名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "高俊保长得好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫小将进前来听奴相告，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘金定、高俊保二过合架枪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "细听奴家说根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你铲平字迹为哪条？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "双锁山中结鸾交。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "情愿同你保皇朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "管教你性命就难逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "山岩诗句留的好"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你若与奴成婚配"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你我一同把山下"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你若不把亲事允"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫头休得来逞强，"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "细听少爷说端详："
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎能与你配鸾凰？"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管叫你枪下一命亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我本堂堂有名将"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若再要胡言讲"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听一言来怒气生，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不由奴家动无名。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘金定、高俊保同起打，快枪。刘金定败下，高俊保拉下场花，下。）"
        }
      ],
