    {
      "scene_index": 8,
      "label": "第八场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘金定",
        "樵夫",
        "高俊保"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（高俊保上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "催马来到山岗上，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘金定上，打过合。四小鬼同上，同托高俊保上桌子。刘金定下。樵夫上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "樵夫",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉今年八十八，一生尚未成过家。娶了一个老伴九十二，我两个人足足一百"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这丫头也不知怎样，把我引到这山岩之上，我是怎生下去？看下面有一老汉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "樵夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何人唤我？"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老伯请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樵夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这个娃娃，怎么跑到山岩上去玩耍？倘若跌将下来，那还了得！"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老伯，你在那里作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "樵夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉在此砍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若大的年纪，怎么还砍呐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "樵夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳。老汉在此砍樵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望求老伯，救我一救。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樵夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要我救你，也倒不难。待我将柴担捆好了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老伯伯你来呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樵夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四小鬼同上，用风旗遮高俊保，樵夫下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不、不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "中了丫头牢笼计，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘金定上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫声小将休逞能，"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘小姐，刘姑娘，你将我放下山来吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫姑娘放你倒也不难，只是姻缘之事如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我从下就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恐怕你还有三心二意，必须对天明誓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我若有三心二意，叫天厌之，天厌之！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众神速退。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四小鬼同下。高俊保自桌下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "山寨摆宴与将军接风。歇兵三日，同下南唐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高俊保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吹牌子。刘金定、高俊保同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
      ],
